WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.210 --> 00:00:07.950
Tinututulan ni Sen. Aimee Marcos ang aplikasyon ni Justice Secretary Jesus Crispin Remulla para maging ombudsman.

2
00:00:08.470 --> 00:00:15.110
Samantala, tinapos na ng Judicial and Bar Council o JBC ang interviews para sa susunod na ombudsman.

3
00:00:15.420 --> 00:00:17.060
Nagpapatrol, Job Manahan.

4
00:00:20.980 --> 00:00:27.840
Apat na araw tumagal ang mga panayam ng Judicial and Bar Council sa mga nagnanais na maging susunod na ombudsman.

5
00:00:28.590 --> 00:00:53.910
Kasama sa labing pitong aplikante, Sinadating Bureau of Internal Revenue o BIR Commissioner Kim Jacinto Henares, Supreme Court Associate Justice Samuel Garland, Retired Supreme Court Associate Justice Mario Lopez, Sandigan Bayan Presiding Justice Geraldine Faith Ekong, Commission on Human Rights Commissioner Beda Epres, at Justice Secretary Jesus Crispin Remulla.

6
00:00:54.270 --> 00:00:57.600
Kabilang sa mga natanong sa kanila ang lifestyle check.

7
00:00:57.840 --> 00:01:08.220
Kungyari, may anak ka, ikaw yung magulang, pag dinonate mo sa kanya, di okay, di ba?

8
00:01:08.340 --> 00:01:12.960
Pero, tatanungin ka, saan mo kinuha yung dinonate mo sa kanya?

9
00:01:13.180 --> 00:01:21.700
I am pro-lifestyle check, but then, the law has to be clear that it is given and granted to the office of the ombudsman.

10
00:01:23.780 --> 00:01:32.000
Pabor din ang mga aplikante na pataliin ang akses ng publiko sa statement of assets, liabilities and net worth o SAL-N..

11
00:01:32.670 --> 00:01:38.070
Pero, anila, hindi dapat ito gamitin para siraan ng isang opisyal ng gobyerno.

12
00:01:38.340 --> 00:01:45.310
Papayagan ko yung pag-issue ng SAL-N kasi that is my advocacy, transparency, accountability and justice.

13
00:01:45.560 --> 00:01:52.880
Basta yung taong humingi ng SAL-N should write a letter of what the intention is.

14
00:01:53.380 --> 00:01:59.060
The problem here is people can be kidnapped if you reveal.

15
00:01:59.840 --> 00:02:04.700
What is there? But it can be done if it is an investigative report.

16
00:02:06.430 --> 00:02:16.270
Ayon naman kay Interior Undersecretary Romeo Benitez, dapat balikan ang Code of Conduct and Ethical Standards for Public Officials kaugnay ng SAL-N.

17
00:02:17.260 --> 00:02:27.120
So, this is one particular aspect of the law that should be the subject of revisit because this has been susceptible to so many interpretations.

18
00:02:27.140 --> 00:02:28.500
That is...

19
00:02:28.760 --> 00:02:40.280
Aplikante rin ang presiding judge ng Daraga Albay MTC na natanong tungkol sa pagiging abogado ng SunWest, isa sa mga malaking contractors ng flood control projects.

20
00:02:40.610 --> 00:02:50.170
I have already severed my employment the year I think 2017. So, I am the in-house counsel of the SunWest there.

21
00:02:50.170 --> 00:03:16.640
I assume the post of the prosecution and after my appointment as the... and later on appointed as the judge, definitely, one who is a judge or a prosecutor must not have any ties to any government officials or individualities that may taint his reputation to being neutral and impartial.

22
00:03:18.650 --> 00:03:25.290
Ayon sa Korte Suprema, linggo ang aabutin bago matapos ang deliberations ng JBC.

23
00:03:25.860 --> 00:03:28.910
They will collate lahat ng...

24
00:03:29.920 --> 00:03:41.520
Meron silang psychological evaluation, yung results ng written exams, yung results ng interview, as well as results ng survey or any of the complaints.

25
00:03:41.520 --> 00:03:44.760
They will rank na the applicants based on the preference of the members.

26
00:03:47.070 --> 00:03:53.700
Samantala, tinatulan ni Senator Aimee Marcos ang aplikasyon ni Remulla para maging ombudsman.

27
00:03:54.340 --> 00:03:59.240
Aniya, bahagi ito ng planong ipakulong si Vice President Sara Duterte.

28
00:03:59.270 --> 00:04:02.360
At ilang kaalyado ni dating Pangulong Rodrigo Duterte.

29
00:04:03.020 --> 00:04:13.440
Kasama si Remulla sa mga sinampahan ng Senadora ng mga kasong administratibo at kriminal sa ombudsman noong Mayo, kaugnay ng pagkakaaresto kay Duterte ng Interpol.

30
00:04:13.980 --> 00:04:19.020
Dahil dito, di pa nabibigyan ng clearance si Remulla para sa kanyang aplikasyon.

31
00:04:19.810 --> 00:04:25.670
So, two sets of cases against Secretary Boying Remulla presently pending before the ombudsman.

32
00:04:25.720 --> 00:04:28.710
Kung paano siya magkakaroon ng clearance from the ombudsman.

33
00:04:29.220 --> 00:04:30.280
Ipilitin talaga.

34
00:04:30.640 --> 00:04:40.320
Trabaho po namin yan eh, to keep the country stable, to prevent violence, to prevent the happening of any untoward acts.

35
00:04:40.850 --> 00:04:50.710
And I think that we were able to peacefully bring him abroad to face the charges against him without hurting anybody physically.

36
00:04:52.670 --> 00:04:58.710
Ayon sa Korte Suprema, kailangang piliin ng Pangulo ang susunod na ombudsman mula sa shortlist.

37
00:04:58.920 --> 00:05:05.580
Bago ang October 25, 2025 o tatlong buwan matapos mabakante ang posisyon.

38
00:05:05.580 --> 00:05:07.600
Job Manahan, ABS-CBN News.

